snippet.textDisplay: Belonging to Bengal, always felt Bangla and Odia have a lot of similarities and an intrinsic sweetness in themselves. And it is not unknown that probably the foremost vacation destination for any Bengali is Puri or as we call it Srikshetra. Not sure but probably, Rangabati echoes the sentiments of a coastal Odia girl who has fallen in love with a tourist visiting the beautiful beach. Lots of Love.
